{"tid":2443951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"運用科興一事，可引導藍絲屌政府","createTime":"2021-03-12T11:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T20:37:25.000Z","uid":78222,"like":29,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"5af82babf0445b6c3466fbc61de086e951ab5130","tid":2443951,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:01:59.000Z","msg":"呢個其實係一個機會黎<br />\n證明政府同支那野係信唔過<br />\n亦證明政府係唔會俾著數香港人<br />\n而打疫苗嘅代價甚至會死/癱<br />\n<br />\n係 我地同藍絲一定唔會係同路人<br />\n我地可以繼續選擇笑佢地笑科興<br />\n但都可以選擇導鳩佢地屌政府 <br />\n<br />\n我地同藍絲唔會係隊友<br />\n但係可以有共同敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3cc742c8d99416493eef5f0e11c7d5d25b578f0","tid":2443951,"uid":125385,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n6857hx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn6857hx.jpg&h=ec5dcbff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3f89694d9e3bf2f7a4db94a74ebf09642e63653","tid":2443951,"uid":78222,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋如果想屌健身唔戴罩嘅人諗清楚<br />\n首先 武漢肺炎係政府唔封關 先會再爆<br />\n一日唔封關 你匿係屋企一世都無用<br />\n依家已經係同武漢肺炎共存嘅狀態<br />\n<br />\n其次 當日宣揚全民健身<br />\n就係為將來作好準備<br />\n無人健身真係得政府最撚開心"},{"pid":"cc1cbfe2ff37868cc6eb239951c30b05a775da40","tid":2443951,"uid":294,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:04:35.000Z","msg":"引導佢哋打針仲好啦<br />\n反正盲迷係唔會醒"},{"pid":"5e07072f09cb3cddf745a71dc3a912a124854796","tid":2443951,"uid":171107,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:05:00.000Z","msg":"太高估佢地，你幾時有見過畜牲識埋怨主人，佢地只不過係有人類身體既畜牲"},{"pid":"84a75fa5a79fcd5929a9963eb17f7f938d1359d1","tid":2443951,"uid":59586,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:05:10.000Z","msg":"佢哋要繼續打 唔好停<br />\n我哋要不停讚科興 啲賤種死得一個得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d59af438b32fd76853f9916093759c08b19812","tid":2443951,"uid":393145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:05:52.000Z","msg":"遲啲先引導得唔得??<br />\n依家仲有百幾萬支科興<br />\n如果佢哋唔打晒先<br />\n政府就會跑數迫我哋打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60678df886f1da521434b4040cee8eaf03f987dd","tid":2443951,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:06:10.000Z","msg":"忠誠廢物邊會"},{"pid":"54c8fd188279ad10754b7a5a19a93ea503b75646","tid":2443951,"uid":90820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:07:46.000Z","msg":"屌黑醫護、屌場地風水唔好、屌時辰八字唔夾<br />\n都唔會屌政府同科興<br />\n多得祖國照顧先有疫苗<br />\n靠外國嗰啲死過人嘅疫苗就死得人多啦"},{"pid":"d9a7ee6512f6e4781b5013161bac7e779d598822","tid":2443951,"uid":78222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc1cbfe2ff37868cc6eb239951c30b05a775da40","tid":2443951,"uid":294,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:04:35.000Z","msg":"引導佢哋打針仲好啦<br />\n反正盲迷係唔會醒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:09:01.000Z","msg":"有一班人會繼續打 唔洗理<br />\n但事實就係有班人都縮緊唔敢打<br />\n藍絲從來都唔係唔理政治<br />\n而係理關乎到自己嘅政治"},{"pid":"528c56912f6396132e03346cf60f925223d4b1df","tid":2443951,"uid":241399,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cc1cbfe2ff37868cc6eb239951c30b05a775da40","tid":2443951,"uid":294,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:04:35.000Z","msg":"引導佢哋打針仲好啦<br />\n反正盲迷係唔會醒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:10:58.000Z","msg":"呢個簡單實際啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010433649a8cb70cbe298d39a96098a40a86a793","tid":2443951,"uid":3553,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:11:11.000Z","msg":"我有個藍到黑嘅就退休嘅老人家都唔信政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話林奠打假疫苗<br />\n又話大陸無建議60歲以上人打<br />\n話香港政府攞佢黎做白老鼠<img src=\"/a